  "texts": [
    "We submitted our fine-tuned Qwen3-4b model and 1-iteration refinement framework for the shared task, along with GPT-4o-mini for our baseline (Table 3).",
    "Upon our submissions, we found that the refinement framework underperformed on the test set compared to the fine-tuned model.",
    "Calculating the averages of these scores (without the readability metrics) showed that the best model was Qwen3-4b-SFT, which we used as our final submission.",
    "The results in Table 2 show that the refinement framework, particularly when iterations n = 1 or n = 3, succeeded in improving generations from the fine-tuned model.",
    "However, a drop was observed on the test set (Table 3)."
